Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.41,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 봇치쨩은 괜찮아~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.86,0:05:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,봇치쨩한테는
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.02,0:05:04.20,Default,,0,0,0,,오리지널송 작사라는\N중요 임무가 있으니까!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,에??
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.36,0:05:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,전에 정했었잖아~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.60,0:05:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,료가 작곡,\N봇치쨩이 작사 하자고!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.42,0:05:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}가사에 피하고 싶은 말이 많다면\N봇치쨩이 쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,2000)\blur5}쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.57,0:05:14.47,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,800)\blur5\t(00,100,\fscx120\fscy120)\t(100,900,\fscx130\fscy130)\alpha&H60&\pos(960,942.5)}쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.70,0:05:15.60,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,800)\blur5\t(00,100,\fscx110\fscy110)\t(100,900,\fscx120\fscy120)\alpha&H60&\pos(960,942.5)}쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.82,0:05:16.52,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(100,600)\blur5\t(00,100,\fscx105\fscy105)\t(100,700,\fscx110\fscy110)\alpha&H60&\pos(960,942.5)}쓰면 되잖아!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(960,980)}Aㅏ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.76,0:05:18.35,Default,,0,0,0,,에~!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.35,0:05:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,료 선배의 곡이라니\N너무 기대돼요!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.23,0:05:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,혹시 벌써\N완성해놓으셨어요?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.97,0:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,아니
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.00,0:05:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,이미지만 솟아나면\N조만간
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.58,0:05:26.24,Default,,0,0,0,,와, 기대된다!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.24,0:05:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,부탁할게, 료~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.39,0:05:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,그리고\N작사 장관님!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.17,0:05:30.58,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 네...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.92,0:05:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨, 엄청난 일도 맡고\N멋지네!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.79,0:05:35.19,Default,,0,0,0,,머..멋져!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.42,0:05:37.97,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 뭐...\N작사 같은 건 식은 죽 먹기...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.97,0:05:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,휙 하면 뿅 하고\N튀어나오죠~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.55,0:05:41.86,Default,,0,0,0,,고토 씨는\N금방 까부는 거 같더라
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.26,0:05:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,히...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.68,0:05:42.94,Default,,0,0,0,,히, 히히...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:43.66,Default,,0,0,0,,히, 히히, 히...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.66,0:05:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,대히트 칠 게 틀림없는\N밴드다운 가사를 써버릴 테니깐요~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.61,0:05:50.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,600)}"다운"...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.94,0:05:51.70,Default,,0,0,0,,히히힣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.70,0:05:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,히힣흐…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.35,0:05:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,에헤헿…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:53.66,Default,,0,0,0,,헤헿헿…
