Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HE4&\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs80\bord6\pos(958.7,981.88)}좋아요{\fs30}\N\N{\fs80}찌거죠오오옷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.02,0:13:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HEF&\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs80\bord6\pos(961.24,980.1)}좋아요{\fs30}\N\N{\fs80}찌거죠오오옷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.06,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\alpha&HFA&\fn양재백두체b\b0\fs80\bord6\pos(958.4,981.98)}좋아요{\fs30}\N\N{\fs80}찌거죠오오옷!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.51,0:14:03.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나한테는\N영상 사이트만 있으면 돼...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.03,0:14:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}고토 씨~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.89,0:14:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}봇치쨩~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.84,0:14:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,SNS는 이제 됐으니까\N그만 돌아와~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.56,0:14:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,괜찮아~?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:14.01,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 옙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.01,0:14:15.43,Default,,0,0,0,,후우~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.43,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼 아사 촬영\N다시 시작하자!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.27,0:14:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,흐음...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.67,0:14:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,좀처럼\N좋은 게 찍히질 않네~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.78,0:14:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 점프 하는 건\N어때요?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.70,0:14:26.30,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs60\pos(736,605)}점프…?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.70,0:14:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,보기에도 좋고
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,각자 꾸밈 없는 느낌이\N나올 거 같은데요!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.76,0:14:29.68,Default,,0,0,0,,그거 좋다!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:31.30,Default,,0,0,0,,키타쨩 천재~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:32.85,Default,,0,0,0,,어느 지식인이 그랬지...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,OP에서 점프하는 애니는\N갓애니라고...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40\bord3\pos(684,838)}오프닝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.42,0:14:36.61,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,600)\fna두리둥실\fs55\pos(736,600)}엩?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.31,0:14:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,즉, 아사에서 점프하면\N갓밴드가 되는 거 아닌지?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}무슨 인과관계인 걸까...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.89,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐라는지\N전혀 모르겠지만...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.87,Default,,0,0,0,,일단 해보자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.06,0:14:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,어, 에...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.39,0:14:47.26,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿5~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.26,0:14:48.25,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿4~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.25,0:14:49.05,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿3~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.05,0:14:49.99,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿2~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:50.90,Default - A,,0,0,0,,﻿1~
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.77,0:14:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}저..점프는 기억에 없는만큼\N해본 적도 없는데!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.29,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,아...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.73,0:14:51.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,400)}아, 아앗...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.70,0:14:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 봇치의 팬티가...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.62,0:14:56.12,Default,,0,0,0,,어마어마한 사진이\N찍혀버렸구마안!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.82,0:14:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,아무 가치도 없는 게\N비치게 해서 죄송합니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.05,0:15:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,지워주십시오...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.04,0:15:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,좀 더 귀여운 반응을\N기대했는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.23,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}점프조차 만족스럽게\N못하는 나란 년...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.44,0:15:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,자, 한 번 더 가자!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.10,0:15:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,좋은데...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.06,0:15:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드다운 느낌에\N청춘스러움이 플러스됐는걸!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.86,0:15:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,사진 데이터\N보내주시면 안 될까요?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.06,0:15:16.60,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 저도...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,응...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.58,0:15:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,밴드다워지기\N시작했어...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.56,0:15:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,인기 밴드라는 꿈에\N또 한 걸음 다가섰네!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.94,0:15:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,결속밴드!\N본격 시동이네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,좋았어~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.47,0:15:29.24,Default,,0,0,0,,여름에\N라이브(미정)이랑
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.24,0:15:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,데모 CD\N배포(미정) 하고~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.41,0:15:33.84,Default,,0,0,0,,겨울에 퍼스트 앨범\N릴리스(미정)!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:37.62,Default,,0,0,0,,시모키타자와에서 태어난\N갬성 터지는 갬성 록밴드가 되자~!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,확정 정보가\N1도 없네요!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.24,0:15:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,아하하...\N그러게!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.83,0:15:43.57,Default,,0,0,0,,아직 완성된 곡도\N없는데!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.57,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,300)}아...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.86,0:15:47.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}자..작사 쪽은\N완전히 까먹고 있었다!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.45,0:15:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,뭐, 그 부분은 료랑\N봇치가 힘내주길 기대하고~
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.83,0:15:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,근데, 어라...?\N료는?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.99,0:15:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,깨닫고 보니\N이미...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.55,0:15:55.64,Default,,0,0,0,,진짜 자유롭게 산다니까...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.25,0:15:57.76,Default,,0,0,0,,그럼\N오늘은 고마웠어!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.76,0:15:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,해산~!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:06.02,Default - Centor,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna입술l\fs60\bord0\c&H23292B&\frz25.97\pos(885,335)}가사 노트
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}시간이\N지나면 지날수록
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.21,0:16:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}가사 난이도가\N오르는 것만 같아...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.47,0:16:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이..이걸 보여줬다가\N싸늘한 반응이 돌아왔다간...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.73,0:16:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니, 괜히 배려받아서\N격려받기라도 했다간...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}나는...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.22,0:16:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이..일단 아무나한테나 보여주고\N반응 좀 살피자...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.60,0:16:19.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}료 씨..가 좋을까?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}료 씨는 괜히 마음에도 없는\N소리는 안 할 거 같고...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs60\bord5\pos(820,280)\frx12\fry4\frz8.804\c&H373533&\3c&HC0B8B8&}료
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs50\bord5\frx12\fry4\frz8.804\c&H373533&\3c&HC0B8B8&\pos(513,442)}아
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.92,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs50\bord5\c&H373533&\3c&H64BA72&\pos(1020,450)\frx12\fry0\frz10.02}잘 부탁드립니다
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.17,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs45\bord5\c&H373533&\3c&H64BA72&\frx0\fry2\pos(1290,830)\frz12.84}봇치예요\N아직 시모키타에 있는데요,\N한 번 써본 가사 혹시\N봐주실 수 있다든가\N괜찮을까요……?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs30\bord0\frx12\fry4\frz8.804\c&HC1B5B4&\3c&HC0B8B8&\pos(720,665)}읽음
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.17,0:16:27.05,Default - Left,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna천생연분\fs50\bord5\c&H373533&\3c&HBDB4B3&\frx2\fry358\frz9.24\pos(730,1005)}여기 있으니까 와
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.20,0:16:26.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아...!\N벌써 읽었네...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.36,0:16:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.88,0:16:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}세...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.29,0:16:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}세..세련된 카페다!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.83,0:16:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}외..외식 같은 건\N한 번도 혼자 해본 적 없어...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.31,0:16:48.82,Default - Right,,0,0,0,,{\fad(10,10)\fna뉴궁서m\fs80\bord5\blur0\c&H5B498E&\3c&HE1CDCC&\frx8\fry348\frz6.676\fscx90\fscy90\t(00,7510,\fscx100\fscy100)\move(1640,325,1680,315,00,7510)}축{\fna펜고딕m\fs50} 개점
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.04,0:16:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}편의점도 그럭저럭\N기합 넣지 않으면 못 들어가는데...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.69,0:16:43.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}가..갑자기\N들어가도 되는 걸까?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.96,0:16:45.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어떻게\N들어가는 거더라...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.50,0:16:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}드라마 같은 데서\N어쨌지!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}핫...!\N아, 분명...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.12,0:16:49.53,Default,,0,0,0,,이...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.53,0:16:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,이..이보셔...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,주인장\N영업하고 있나아...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.58,0:16:54.95,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 봇치\N여기야, 여기
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.55,0:17:04.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}어..어색하다...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.49,0:17:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그러고 보니 료 씨랑\N단둘이 만나는 건 처음이었을지도...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.14,0:17:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아직도 좀체\N어떤 사람인지 모르겠고...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}그보다...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.92,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}왜..왜 아무 말도\N안 해주는 걸까!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.77,0:17:15.06,Default,,0,0,0,,잘 먹었습니다
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.06,0:17:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}다..다 먹었네!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.49,0:17:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}에, 어..어쩌지?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.53,0:17:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}내가 먼저\N말 꺼내면 되는 걸까...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.41,0:17:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}아니, 그래도...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.62,0:17:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}아까 촬영\N즐거웠죠!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.65,0:17:23.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5}딱히
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.25,0:17:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(00,00)\blur5\c&HFBD1FF&\3c&H985BFF&}이렇게 될지도\N모르는데~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.43,0:17:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,얼른 가사나 보여줘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.91,0:17:41.87,Default,,0,0,0,,아, 옙
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.17,0:17:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,부탁드립니다...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.42,0:17:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,음, 어디 봐보겠소
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.42,0:17:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,와...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.76,0:17:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,오오어어엇...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.92,0:17:45.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(959.9,979.06)}오오어어엇...!
